{"tid":762153,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"與曼聯高層不和 摩帥拒出席記招","createTime":"2018-07-31T04:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T12:56:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"11189835c530499c27c142e46cfa8a51d5852af2","tid":762153,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"正在美國參加國際冠軍杯的曼聯將於明早鬥皇家馬德里，惟曼聯主帥摩連奴對行政總裁活華特的引援進度非常不滿，加上上場被利物浦大炒，摩帥決定不出席賽前新聞記者會以表不滿。摩帥稱早前已開出了一份5人收購名單，但高層並沒引進任何一人。<br />\n<br />\n另外據報摩佬希望踢畢世界杯的球員能提前一周歸隊，幫助他應對季初人員不足的危機：「我希望有人能令拉舒福特和菲爾鍾斯提前結束假期，回到陣中幫助球隊，因為在賽季初我們已有麻煩了。」"},{"pid":"e76ae7ef420245e3c29e8513d20638b4f5be53fe","tid":762153,"uid":34264,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:50:50.000Z","msg":"球會逼害!<br />\n球員逼害!<br />\n球證逼害!<br />\n賽會逼害!<br />\n摩狗失敗原因=全世界逼害!"},{"pid":"7544420805ca872dce574873f22c4463ea8ca693","tid":762153,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"木仔係鬼！"},{"pid":"86e0b5271e610e95606e72b898f6adf38ba72d1e","tid":762153,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c2fc5812fdcae60ee2e43a4edba1c83e523748","tid":762153,"uid":187076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/130510_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F130510_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a324a2cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c09a4e5a44582777253033b97f11b23694dc889f","tid":762153,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"摩佬好快玩撚完"},{"pid":"434724feb7172f355f8420ef9c80e9ef88b03da5","tid":762153,"uid":10249,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:08:44.000Z","